## Reach & Frequency Analysis Workflow

Analyze and optimize reach and frequency:

- [ ] 1. **Define parameters**: Establish target audience size, campaign duration, and budget for {{client_name}}
- [ ] 2. **Set frequency goals**: Determine optimal frequency range based on campaign objective (awareness: 3-5x, consideration: 5-8x, conversion: 8-12x)
- [ ] 3. **Model reach curves**: Estimate unduplicated reach at different budget levels using GRP-based or platform-native models
- [ ] 4. **Frequency distribution**: Map expected frequency distribution (1x, 2x, 3x+) across {{target_audience}}
- [ ] 5. **Effective reach calculation**: Calculate 1+ reach, 3+ reach (effective), and excessive frequency (10+)
- [ ] 6. **Cross-channel deduplication**: Estimate duplicated vs. unduplicated reach across channels
- [ ] 7. **Budget scenarios**: Model reach/frequency outcomes at 3 budget levels (conservative, recommended, stretch)
- [ ] 8. **Frequency cap recommendations**: Set platform-level frequency caps to minimize waste

## Key Inputs
- Client: {{client_name}}
- Target audience: {{target_audience}}
- Budget: {{budget}}
- Campaign duration: {{campaign_duration}}
- Channels: {{channels}}
